story_menu_76411=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >我</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >們要走啦</font><font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >！</font>
story_menu_76412=<font face="Default" color="#ffffff" >二位為何要對我痛下殺手？</font>
